Cepta slowly stood up and looked at Wildrider and Dead-End, and then looked 
back down at herself. Her body had no markings for any faction; it was just 
yellow and black, like a centepede. Cepta was a bit confused when she 
watched Wildrider stick a hand in Dead-End's face. She wasn't sure what to 
say, so she kept quiet.
